# Optional. If set, the "AI Insights" feature calls Claude to generate
# real optimization recommendations. Without it, the app falls back to a
# built-in heuristic engine so the demo still works end-to-end.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# --- Real Meta Marketing API (NOT used in the demo / mock mode) ---
# When you wire up the real Meta Marketing API later, these are the values
# you would provide. The data layer in lib/meta/client.ts is the single
# place to swap mock data for real API calls.
# META_APP_ID=
# META_APP_SECRET=
# META_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# META_AD_ACCOUNT_ID=act_xxxxxxxxxx
